Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.81,0:00:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SERN will take the time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SERN? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makise Kurisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.41,0:00:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe Rintarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.94,0:00:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hashida Itaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You three are coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.30,0:00:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina Mayuri is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.74,0:00:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...not needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.40,0:00:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.64,0:00:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.10,0:00:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For FB... FB... FB...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.60,0:01:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.23,0:01:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.18,0:01:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.09,0:01:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe, get away from her!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.58,0:01:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll kill you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.43,0:01:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pay for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.63,0:01:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make her pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.21,0:02:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,42.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CRT.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.24,0:02:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.47,0:02:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.27,0:02:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if it fails...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.72,0:02:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.81,0:04:31.81,Title1,,0000,0000,0000,,Metaphysics Necrosis
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mayuri was still in elementary school
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.72,0:04:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}when her grandmother died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.18,0:04:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She went to the grave every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.86,0:04:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even six months after her grandmother's death,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.58,0:04:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}she was still going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She always had her grandmother's \Npocket watch in her hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and she was always, always looking up at the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like she was waiting for \Nher grandmother to come and get her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.46,0:05:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then one day, there was a ray of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was the kind called Rembrandt Lighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.22,0:05:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}or an angel's ladder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.16,0:05:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It felt like the light was drawing her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like she was going to disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.02,0:05:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.53,0:05:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let it take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to be my hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use you for human experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.47,0:05:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The words that came out of my mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.77,0:05:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}were from some show I'd seen as a little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mayuri and I had watched it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Some mad scientist, screaming like an idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.72,0:06:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Mayushii is your hostage, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I guess I can't go, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.94,0:06:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you napping?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.14,0:06:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What time is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.27,0:06:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost five.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going shopping, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:06:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shopping...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll order pizza.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't get the tropical special.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.35,0:07:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.35,0:07:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time leap worked?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.02,0:07:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.13,0:07:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Mayuri? Where is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.94,0:07:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii said she was going to Miss Ruka's, \Nto invite her to the party, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The development conference is canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Canceled?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.62,0:07:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.77,0:07:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're done here for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you, go home now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.34,0:07:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay? Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His phone starts ringing, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Mayushii.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't answer the phone right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:07:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like to leave a message...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's nothing to indicate \Nthat the world line changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's different than the D-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really am back at 5:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the bullet train!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the bullet train is white.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After this, Mayuri will return with Suzuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Should I go to the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, who'd believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.93,0:08:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That I've come from the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Three hours left...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.31,0:08:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oka... No, Kyouma—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.76,0:08:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Mayuri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.28,0:08:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Left?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thirty minutes ago, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she was going back to the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't she get back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.06,0:08:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:09:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so nice of you to \Ninvite me to the party, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.76,0:09:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she say she was stopping anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.84,0:09:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you see her, tell her to call me right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.24,0:09:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If the world line hasn't changed,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}then if I don't do anything different,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}she should do the same things as last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.55,0:09:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyan-nyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.70,0:09:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feyris can't answer the phone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you need something...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.27,0:09:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.67,0:09:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assistant...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.45,0:09:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, we're done today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You time leaped from the future, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.85,0:10:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second you answered the phone, \Nyou seemed to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.97,0:10:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the way you're acting,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can guess that something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have time to give you the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just run.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get away from the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me later, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Tell Daru, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe Rintarou!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's Ochanomizu—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.89,0:10:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Mayuri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She just invited me to your party—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.77,0:10:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.43,0:10:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn right, up there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.51,0:10:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, which way is Ochanomizu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.72,0:10:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to take Nae shopping...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask at the police box!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And once you've taken her, don't come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.06,0:10:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.67,0:11:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.04,0:11:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! It's the first star!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.25,0:11:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the party?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's canceled. I told Kurisu and Daru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.81,0:11:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I asked Suzu-san to come, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Daru-kun was ordering pizza...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii doesn't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always do things I don't understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but today, I really don't understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really want to \Ndo the experiment, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.96,0:12:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.86,0:12:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But just for now, can you listen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.66,0:12:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain the details later, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Mayushii just got scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.93,0:12:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rush hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no one's at the platform...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once again,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the following lines have been shut down, \Ndue to a bomb threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said they don't know when \Nthe trains will start again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:13:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.12,0:13:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.23,0:13:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri, get to the subway now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe Rintarou, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you standing there for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.63,0:13:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, as fast as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.34,0:13:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.10,0:14:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina Mayuri was the one who died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.46,0:14:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.55,0:14:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Okabe Rintarou has been captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.02,0:14:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.03,0:14:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1809)}Mayuri, I will save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.37,0:14:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Canceled?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.18,0:14:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got word
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that Mr. Braun is planning to return tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin, did you do something again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.67,0:14:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:15:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're done here for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was I too forceful?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.28,0:15:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.43,0:15:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It doesn't matter if I was acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For now, I just need them away from the lab!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.15,0:15:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Mayushii.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't answer the phone right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.14,0:15:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is it taking so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's going to end up like last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I need to find Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.85,0:15:32.31,CellphoneR,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukako
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukako! It's me! Okabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oka... I'm sorry, Kyouma—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.18,0:15:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Mayuri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Mayuri there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.60,0:15:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just heading bac—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.08,0:15:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell her not to move until I get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she was going back to the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do as I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.62,0:15:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.09,0:15:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.58,0:16:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the bullet train!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the bullet train is white.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.60,0:16:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.29,0:16:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was about to go fix Fubuki-chan's costume,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.99,0:16:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then go to the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.03,0:16:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fubuki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cosplay friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.31,0:16:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said a thread on the costume \NI made came undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just got a message from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.39,0:16:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.27,0:16:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once it's fixed, I'll go right to the lab,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll make it to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.71,0:16:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. The party...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.73,0:16:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The party was cancel...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it was postponed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.61,0:16:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't use the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.66,0:16:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I wanted you to come with me for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.64,0:16:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Fubuki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.63,0:17:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but do it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.46,0:17:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we're going to be away for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.73,0:17:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On a trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Together?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.52,0:17:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can put Fubuki-chan off till tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this is very sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.66,0:17:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have much time to catch the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.54,0:17:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Mayushii isn't ready at all, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.28,0:17:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.93,0:17:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Akihabara Station that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're taking the subway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:17:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a really long time
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since you pulled me along like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.64,0:18:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.97,0:18:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.08,0:18:57.35,Sign13B,,0000,0000,0000,,From: Assistant \NSubject: Did something happen? \N\NTell me later, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.73,0:19:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurisu, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My watch isn't working...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wound it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.69,0:19:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sobu line shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut down?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.07,0:19:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.87,0:19:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bomb threat was called in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.38,0:19:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Okarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.90,0:19:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii has a lot of places she wants to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.05,0:19:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's okay for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when this is over, \NI want you to tell me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.07,0:20:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.42,0:20:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.65,0:20:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I can't help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have that party sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.75,0:20:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.11,0:20:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometime...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.28,0:20:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri-oneechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.25,0:21:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.21,0:21:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to surprise her...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.98,0:21:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.77,0:22:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.32,0:22:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...save Mayuri!
